{
  "stem": "17426.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just male, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were brought-- excuse me-- to a Baustelle, which is workplace, where a German company by the name of [INAUDIBLE] was laying rails from west to east, and bogs, watered-- water-logged bogs which we had to dry out by bringing from in other areas sand and soil in order to fill it in.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was our work for the next year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was assigned-- again fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fortunately, I was assigned to the kitchen because when I was transported, the administrator of the Jews to be delivered to Poznan-- his was Neumann, Dr.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Neumann.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he saw me, and he called me for some reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know why, but he called me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He asked my name, and he asked me what I do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there wasn't time to explain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't take time to explain when you were called before a-- a Nazi, you knew that nothing good is coming out of.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he asked me what I do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, I'm a dentist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't say I'm a student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm a dentist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he says, when you come to camp, you report to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I feared what will happen, what he'll do to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father said, well, he won't remember you, even when he gets to camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But anyhow, when we came to camp, he remembered me, and the following-- in the morning when we were supposed to go to work, he had already at that time chosen police.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one of the policemen by the name of Chaim Tszan, who was also a town-person of mine-- he called that the dentist should report to-- He didn't even know who he was calling, but he knew me.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he-- the dentist should report to Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Neumann.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
